# GeoStock AI — environment variables
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` (or `.env`) and replace the placeholder
# values with your own keys. Everything below is optional — the dashboard
# runs without any keys (Gemini falls back to a heuristic tagger, GNews
# falls back to NewsAPI, and NewsAPI falls back to a curated offline
# sample), but live data needs at least Gemini + one news provider.
#
# Never commit your real keys. `.env*` is gitignored except for this file.

# Google Gemini — required for AI severity tagging + ticker analysis +
# event-detail panels + the streaming analyst chatbot.
# Get a free key at https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# GNews — primary geopolitical news source (100 req/day free).
# Sign up at https://gnews.io
GNEWS_API_KEY=your_gnews_api_key_here

# NewsAPI — fallback when GNews is unreachable / over quota (100 req/day free).
# Sign up at https://newsapi.org
NEWS_API_KEY=your_newsapi_key_here
